  "body": "Right now the `tiller` deployment only exposes port `44134` (as you can see [here](https://github.com/kubernetes/helm/blob/master/cmd/helm/installer/install.go#L141)).\r\n\r\nTiller exposes probes and metrics in `44135`. Because tiller doesn't expose that port and does not contain any Prometheus annotations, making Prometheus scrape tiller is a bit more complex.\r\n\r\nBy adding port `44135` we can automatically make Prometheus scrape tiller and fetch those metrics.",
